OL,3,CMeet all 11 candidates running in
OL,4,CGuernsey by-election
OL,6,FNominations for Guernsey's by-election
OL,7,Fhave closed after a three-day
OL,8,Fsubmission period.
OL,10,FEleven candidates who are looking to
OL,11,Ffill the disgraced ex-politician
OL,12,FJonathan Le Tocq's former States seat
OL,13,Fare now confirmed.
OL,15,FLe Tocq's seat in the States has been
OL,16,Fvacant since December last year, when
OL,17,Fhe resigned after admitting to 15
OL,18,Fsexual offences, including possessing
OL,19,Fmore than 2,400 indecent images of
OL,20,Fchildren.
