OL,3,CMeet all 11 candidates running in
OL,4,CGuernsey by-election
OL,6,FThe former politician was jailed for
OL,7,Fnine years in January.
OL,9,FThe by-election will take place on
OL,10,FWednesday, 29 April, with the
OL,11,Felectoral roll closing four days
OL,12,Fbeforehand.
OL,14,FThis will be the first by-election to
OL,15,Fuse the island-wide voting system.
OL,17,FThe candidates running are:
OL,19,FAll islanders who registered to vote
OL,20,Fin last year's general election will
OL,21,Fremain eligible to vote.
