OL,3,CMeet all 11 candidates running in
OL,4,CGuernsey by-election
OL,6,FAnyone who has since become eligible,
OL,7,For otherwise wishes to register to
OL,8,Fvote, can do so online.
OL,10,FResidents can cast their ballots in
OL,11,Fperson at the following locations:
OL,13,FAlternatively, islanders can register
OL,14,Ffor postal votes up to Friday 10 April.
OL,16,FProspective Deputies will have the
OL,17,Fsame expenditure limit as those who
OL,18,Fstood in the general election: up to
OL,19,F#3,000 on their campaign.
