OL,3,CMeet all 11 candidates running in
OL,4,CGuernsey by-election
OL,6,FCandidate manifestos will only be
OL,7,Fpublished on the States' election
OL,8,Fwebsite; there will be no centralised
OL,9,Fphysical booklet.
OL,11,FGuernsey States' and Constitutions
OL,12,FCommittee (SACC) estimates the total
OL,13,Fcost of holding this year's by-
OL,14,Felection will be #75,000.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
